WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:01:03.463 --> 00:01:06.199
Qilai North Peak 1.2K

00:01:06.199 --> 00:01:09.185
That's Qilai Main Peak over there

00:01:11.171 --> 00:01:15.241
Taroko Mountain, Mount Patoru

00:01:15.291 --> 00:01:16.676
Keep going!!

00:02:08.027 --> 00:02:09.028
They're over there

00:02:12.215 --> 00:02:13.700
Going up there is very energy-intensive!!

00:02:14.384 --> 00:02:15.902
Bring out my secret weapon

00:03:17.280 --> 00:03:18.531
Hooray!! We're up!!

00:03:29.125 --> 00:03:30.677
Qilai North Peak!!

00:04:47.003 --> 00:04:47.954
Hehuan Mountain

00:04:50.239 --> 00:04:51.774
Sacred Ridge!!

00:04:54.777 --> 00:04:56.529
Mount Patoru, Mount Taroko

00:05:01.351 --> 00:05:02.302
Qilai Main Peak

00:05:05.154 --> 00:05:05.938
Golden Wing White Eyebrow

00:05:06.756 --> 00:05:09.409
Now leaving Qilai North Peak for the Big Tooth

00:05:13.696 --> 00:05:14.630
Keep going!! Good!!

00:05:25.508 --> 00:05:26.876
After passing Qilai North Peak

00:05:27.377 --> 00:05:29.962
Continuing east for 1.7km

00:05:29.962 --> 00:05:31.364
This is the Crescent Pool campsite.

00:05:32.365 --> 00:05:34.734
This route is the Qilai East Ridge route.

00:05:35.668 --> 00:05:39.439
However, our trip is to reach the front tooth in the direction of Pingfeng Mountain to the north.

00:05:40.456 --> 00:05:43.943
So we will turn north at the fork in the road on the Qilai North Peak Grassland.

00:05:44.660 --> 00:05:46.946
follow the ridge line to the front tooth.

00:06:50.376 --> 00:06:52.428
Looks like we're going down this way.

00:06:54.080 --> 00:06:55.164
We just went down this way.

00:06:58.468 --> 00:07:01.454
Now we have to... walk over!!

00:07:01.454 --> 00:07:02.755
Actually, this part is a bit like...

00:07:03.823 --> 00:07:05.525
Mount Shinada

00:07:07.026 --> 00:07:09.645
The route down Mount Shinada along the Seiryo Ridge.

00:07:10.146 --> 00:07:11.547
Somewhat like it

00:07:12.265 --> 00:07:13.816
There are stacked stones on the road

00:07:14.383 --> 00:07:15.885
You should turn here

00:07:23.059 --> 00:07:24.093
From beside the big rock

00:07:24.944 --> 00:07:26.195
Then come all the way like this

00:07:28.314 --> 00:07:29.482
go down here...

00:07:34.137 --> 00:07:34.670
Stacked stones

00:08:00.563 --> 00:08:02.381
That's the gap between my front teeth.

00:09:44.717 --> 00:09:45.868
It's so high up here!

00:09:56.879 --> 00:09:59.882
We just cut down from there.

00:10:05.454 --> 00:10:06.222
Goodbye front teeth!!

00:10:07.139 --> 00:10:09.508
Now we need to climb back!!

00:10:11.427 --> 00:10:12.561
Now we need to climb back!!

00:10:20.086 --> 00:10:21.120
Go Go!!

00:10:37.887 --> 00:10:38.771
Climb up!!

00:10:53.786 --> 00:10:55.755
Wow~ Awesome!!

00:10:58.507 --> 00:11:01.027
Now we need to descend North Peak to our campsite.

00:11:01.027 --> 00:11:02.712
Our camp is over there.

00:11:03.112 --> 00:11:04.797
On the way down North Peak.

00:11:05.297 --> 00:11:08.167
We encountered a rescue helicopter circling low.

00:11:09.018 --> 00:11:11.420
I wonder if they are on a search mission.

00:11:12.088 --> 00:11:13.589
Hope everything goes well.

00:11:15.191 --> 00:11:18.194
Something might have happened.

00:11:26.819 --> 00:11:29.488
What's the big deal?

00:11:29.488 --> 00:11:32.475
He's still looking, still searching.

00:11:34.960 --> 00:11:36.045
After returning to camp.

00:11:36.395 --> 00:11:39.014
He fetched water from the stream below the Qilai Mountain Hut.

00:11:39.582 --> 00:11:41.767
The water here is clear and icy cold.

00:11:42.718 --> 00:11:43.703
Water source spotted!!

00:11:44.470 --> 00:11:45.254
Flowing water!!

00:12:03.389 --> 00:12:07.410
Go down from the Qilai Mountain Hut to fetch water.

00:12:07.410 --> 00:12:09.245
Climb down to the valley.

00:12:10.279 --> 00:12:11.964
About fifteen minutes.

00:12:12.548 --> 00:12:14.583
It took about fifteen minutes to get back.

00:12:15.084 --> 00:12:16.986
Hmm...

00:12:17.737 --> 00:12:18.888
Great!! I'm a water tycoon!

00:12:20.923 --> 00:12:22.358
I can have a big meal tonight!

00:12:29.482 --> 00:12:31.117
This is a behind-the-scenes clip from the video.

00:12:31.784 --> 00:12:33.953
Today's chef...Ade!!

00:12:40.292 --> 00:12:41.427
Chef Annie!!

00:12:41.427 --> 00:12:45.114
Chef Annie's sausage!!

00:12:47.066 --> 00:12:49.752
Ni: I'm not the chef!! I'm not the chef!!

00:12:49.752 --> 00:12:51.320
Sakura: Hurry up!! Chef!!

00:12:51.320 --> 00:12:52.922
Ni: I'm a self-taught chef. (Are these chopsticks?)

00:12:53.823 --> 00:12:55.591
Okay...are you going to give it to me?

00:12:56.108 --> 00:12:57.943
Sakura: Are you going to take a picture of me!? (Oh!! Okay~)

00:12:58.627 --> 00:12:59.445
Okay!! (Cute~)

00:12:59.528 --> 00:13:01.063
Sakura: Chef, over here!!

00:13:02.047 --> 00:13:02.965
Ni: Eat first, eat first, eat it all!!

00:13:02.982 --> 00:13:04.066
Sakura: Do you want one!? I'll give you one.

00:13:06.235 --> 00:13:07.603
Still have some (It's okay)

00:13:07.720 --> 00:13:08.871
Lamb hot pot!

00:13:09.205 --> 00:13:10.322
Lamb hot pot!

00:13:10.322 --> 00:13:12.208
Ni: Turns out there were no duck meatballs with the lamb!!

00:13:12.508 --> 00:13:13.676
De: There's still lamb.

00:13:13.676 --> 00:13:14.860
Ni: Almost all gone!! XD

00:13:17.880 --> 00:13:19.965
De: @##%$^@!

00:13:20.082 --> 00:13:21.350
Ni: You weren't here just now~ Otherwise, the pot would have just been opened.

00:13:21.417 --> 00:13:22.551
De: Meat... bring the meat up.

00:13:25.604 --> 00:13:27.656
Lamb hot pot noodles... lamb noodles!!

00:13:32.878 --> 00:13:34.647
I just went to the toilet.

00:13:35.714 --> 00:13:38.934
Then we found the water deer!!

00:13:42.588 --> 00:13:43.289
Mythical beasts!!

00:13:47.209 --> 00:13:47.810
(◎_◎;) Ooh ooh!!

00:13:54.233 --> 00:13:56.001
One? Two? Three?

00:13:56.519 --> 00:13:59.522
Four, five, six, seven?

00:13:59.805 --> 00:14:00.990
Eight!!

00:14:23.946 --> 00:14:26.949
The tent's reflection?

00:14:44.633 --> 00:14:47.636
The wind is really strong tonight!! I went to the internet cafe to see Windy.

00:14:50.005 --> 00:14:51.056
11 degrees Celsius

00:14:53.242 --> 00:14:54.260
Level 5 gusts!?

00:14:54.260 --> 00:14:55.244
So this is what a level 5 gust is~

00:14:55.628 --> 00:14:56.812
It really is strong!!

00:15:10.659 --> 00:15:17.866
A deer blocking the way!?

00:15:17.866 --> 00:15:21.820
Deer: Give it to me!! (chewing)

00:15:31.463 --> 00:15:32.247
Bye-bye!!

00:15:37.937 --> 00:15:39.805
Can I take a picture!?

00:15:43.158 --> 00:15:44.977
Take a picture!! Take a picture~

00:15:47.947 --> 00:15:50.933
Deer: Wait!! I came out and struck a pose.

00:16:37.329 --> 00:16:39.648
Is that Ade!? (Yes)

00:16:40.232 --> 00:16:43.619
Hehehe...How long have you been standing here!?

00:16:44.203 --> 00:16:45.637
It's 5:51 AM now.

00:16:45.637 --> 00:16:47.990
Time to collect the bill and get ready to leave.
114
00:16:50,142 --&gt; 00:1651,126 
Say something!

00:16:51.393 --> 00:16:52.928
Sakura: I really want to go home~

00:16:52.928 --> 00:16:54.396
Okay!! We're going home!! (Thank you)

00:17:58.060 --> 00:17:59.928
Complete!! (I've finally finished!!)

00:17:59.928 --> 00:18:01.914
Yeah!! Awesome!! (Two Hundred Peaks)

00:18:06.101 --> 00:18:08.137
Kirai-chu!! Kirai-hoku!!

00:18:08.754 --> 00:18:09.521
Pingfeng Mountain!!

00:18:10.906 --> 00:18:14.093
This time, Qilai is mainly in the north...

00:18:14.960 --> 00:18:16.445
To the front teeth!!

00:18:16.445 --> 00:18:17.946
We're done~

00:18:18.614 --> 00:18:20.749
Well... that's all for today~

00:18:21.333 --> 00:18:21.817
Bye-bye!!

